commit_message:
Better code quality, less dependency. (#12)

* Removed the dependency on opencv

The project's dependencies on opencv are sparse and this makes `Propagator`'s logic consistent with `smooth_filter`.

* Redundant code removed.

* Duplicated code in examples merged. Better timing.
Convert torch models to pytorch models (listed in TODOs). Rename the layers according to the origin paper.
Bugfix: The propagator fails to process images with alpha channels
PhotoWCT CPU support. Pure CPU mode is ~10x slower.
Add the submodule for model files. Fix demos.
Add a converter which shows how to convert old torch models into pytorch models.
More info about model loading & converting

Scripted pretrained model download (#24)

* Script to download models

* Model download bash script, usage explained

Bug fixing & add cuda options (#28)

* Fix an incorrect number.

* Add CUDA options
Add photo_wct.pth to the main repo
Update docker image and pynvrtc interface code
Add credit to Marco Forte for the compute lapacian function.
